{"tid":1476062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"思路清晰 阻你少少時間 請入來睇一睇","createTime":"2019-08-15T16:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:38:53.000Z","uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"381c843f025b812e25be655cd44a33cd25c0c616","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">小不忍則亂大謀，我好同意呢位絲打嘅睇法，佢思路幾清晰，個人認為幾有道理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n的確而家我地咪鬼引開左，亦都因為鬼做咗啲失民意嘅事。就好似絲打嘅第五段所講，而家警方唔做清場，目的就係想我哋失民意，咁反而反映出我哋中咗警方計。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且，最近我哋可能真係比憤怒支配左我哋嘅頭腦，開始有失控嘅情況出現，所以我哋更加應該要控制返自己情緒，唔可以將香港推向一個懸崖邊，萬一推到去懸崖邊，只會令我地呢班手足承受返個後果。所以基本上我哋應該要變得更加團結，先可以對抗暴政。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n見到佢都好落力推po比大家睇，但好似冇乜成效，希望我呢位P牌仔幫到佢。<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割席 不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBrMwfM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBrMwfM.png&h=701dcf25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKccrO7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKccrO7.png&h=89d07147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原po link:<br />\n[重po]經過812同813我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1473460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1473460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"27f4658a468051e5cbac809bb51a9b4ce3c60c5b","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:26:15.000Z","msg":"原文:<br />\n雖然我都係一個P牌，我知你會諗「P牌仔出po，此po已完」個啲，但我都想你花幾分鐘睇下我對今次運動嘅分析。有咩不滿任你鬧，隨便負評。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n812，個個都係到屌鳩散水撚，其實分化現象開始出現。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當時我都係現場，有人行嚟同我講有防暴部署緊喇，睇時機好走。而且的確我係走左，但我覺得正正係走左，所以812先贏得徹底。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同我講話走嘅，其實都係兄弟，佢地係想話比大家聽有危險，都係有五大訴求係心入面，都係希望大家不被捕不受傷。佢地咁樣嘅舉動，都係想大家安全，做到真正嘅be water，但係卻被標籤為「散水撚」。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣真係唔係分化咩？大家唔係話不分化，不割蓆咩？<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實你地口中講嘅散水撚先係指出危險嘅人。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我明白到前線會好灰，後面比啲「散水撚」搞到冇左後援，更加易比啲狗包抄 。所以我覺得要解決惡意散水撚嘅問題<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">第一，佢地需要分析現時嘅情況 同埋散嘅原因 同埋假設性嘅結局。<br />\n第二，要係現埸進行討論 睇下大眾嘅建議。<br />\n要留一齊留，要走一齊走 <br />\n避免前線比人賣嘅情況出現</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同樣嘅道理，「冷氣軍師」同「P牌仔」係唔係比你地呢班冇P或甩P嘅分化緊？<span style=\"font-size: large;\">因為有啲五毛申請咗連登ac，五毛po上到熱門，就決定唔比P牌評分，反而扼殺咗一啲真係想比意見嘅P牌</span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">咁點解唔好好咁善用不推文回覆？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗深一層我地會唔會係中左五毛計？如果真係因為一啲五毛就禁P牌聲，我地只會接收到更少嘅意見，亦都係心理戰方面輸左，因為原來五毛就可以分化到各位巴絲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而係813呢日，大家比憤怒支配左頭腦，因為覺得佢係鬼，我地就捉左佢 ，令到失左民意，連外國記者都對我地失望。假如我地今日捉左隻鬼 ，同埋動左私刑，咁我地同佔中七警仲有咩分別 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申我對捉鬼冇咩意見。但我地有冇咁嘅必要去捉鬼咩？捉到咁又點？<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一隻鬼就令到我地咁，咁我地唔係中左警犬計咩？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「鬼其實都做唔到啲咩，主要係心理壓力，等我哋疑神疑鬼，互相分化」</span><br />\n大家諗下，即使有犬扮人係大家身邊，佢地係機場，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">附近又冇速龍防暴部署嘅時候，得幾個鬼做得啲咩？就算佢地真係㩒你落地，有拘捕行動嘅時候，大家合力好似今日打到隻狗仆街。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">若然要捉鬼，到不如大家認清啲鬼同人嘅分別，唔好單靠一啲估計去認係人定鬼</span></span>，例如 大隻（Rock Gor Story個男人）、帶咩手鏈（何韻詩助手）。到現今時勢，警察用扮示威者尼招，我明白到前線嘅心理負擔都大，對其他人嘅警戒心強，但係希望前線去理性諗每一樣野，我唔希望有反效果嘅出現。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上我個人覺得，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家警方唔做清埸，目的係想等我地嘅民意下降 ，用民意牌去壓制呢埸運動。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反而其實係機場，只要我地人數多，就可以令到機場停飛，而唔需要用到阻旅客入口。咁樣<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一來唔使比啲旅客覺得係我地直接阻到佢地上唔到機，二來民意方面又可以加一分。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣嘅就係，大家都係有種仇警心態，而我都明白原因，只不過大家唔好抱住一個有殺錯冇放過嘅心態，對住一啲可能支持大家嘅警察都屌咁。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">我個人認為可以針對翻一啲真正嘅黑警，執法有問題嘅犬，例如情緒管理惡劣，執法手段有問題嘅，分翻開警察同警犬，並唔係地圖炮咁殺。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我咁樣講，可能會俾你地覺得我係幫佢地洗白，但係若然警察部門入面，有良知嘅走曬，成個警隊得翻一種聲音，咁樣到時我地就會失去左呢個出來指控嘅聲音。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以警方識派鬼去分化我地，我地都應該同時用警察同警犬嘅區別分化翻佢地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且經過今晚，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地應該反省翻今日嘅不完善，並作出改善，例如係民間記者會上向一眾</span></span>旅客致歉，亦都係機場入面再次致歉，取回民意。我一直認為民意同經濟制裁，係唯一逼使到政府妥協嘅關鍵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上純粹個人意見，大家可以諗下。<br />\n我並非分化割蓆亦非篤灰，只係想指出今次運動出現梗嘅問題，同時提出改善嘅方法，亦都唔希望我地係呢場運動付出過嘅所有嘢，最終會得唔到我地應得嘅回報，感謝你花你嘅時間來睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非與勇武派同一戰線，永不分化！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望終有一日，我哋可以除低曬所有gear，係煲底擁抱一下。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n#毋忘五大訴求<br />\n#Free HongKong"},{"pid":"fa192f2c87c60789fc1ce165eac795785e384179","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d719ae303c41067bfb73f39174e5d7195f6a54b8","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:26:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4b1f75989e9731700544c63f5e07a52f19b4a1","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"721 721 721 721 721 721"},{"pid":"617f05067811305dd64cea2b286192def8a1580a","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"811 811 811 811 811 811 811"},{"pid":"aca0d24ad57ecab33129c032ee2f1100c4ff38ef","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:27:27.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"6d6cf696ad25ee9f3162cec5e9a094bec268608e","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7q4RHqy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7q4RHqy.jpg&h=12908c4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"801c019f27b4a120164ce989f3edcdd80f9889a2","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Xvmkcj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Xvmkcj.jpg&h=6d1bf4b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5y4aXYZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5y4aXYZ.jpg&h=710b7271&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZXMHO5F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZXMHO5F.jpg&h=d5a91dac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ydyVLF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ydyVLF.jpg&h=f6ae3bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0itZRi0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0itZRi0.jpg&h=02bf2d06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgdOKD0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgdOKD0.jpg&h=be3db93f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c067587d9afcb4c05f1f316ca0c9b88ecfe51639","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7f2e27ef6533a7604f24d4f212b7a5e278e360","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:29:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f133c80dffd11a5433bacc34173dd6ae79fb06","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"十連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82944fb1c988076927c691b5823f5574dbef0999","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5349bde0fce3485b9260e457347d3535af203dc0","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:31:45.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1530ddaa3846e1fd7b5831ebf3447b3102742fc8","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:32:08.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c06ca6b83df11f5fdaaea96133548475ef824d92","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:32:31.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"fc3830691593bfcb7970a85d3e2ea72ab4856fee","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"e5100a10c4f5ec223f27a00396d62a6713e9a1e6","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:33:18.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"1208516efbe135b4131f02b77c39a77b3db38e3f","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"7c502d22f9e833bc5e9dd34fc69379c96692d7eb","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"38992bfb6442b107cd3f7f7decb3163d8383f175","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7a04204b0efe846370debae5080c6a9033e224b5","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:35:05.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"1a0cab7b7bcc66e133c9586f03696f42097001ab","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"11"},{"pid":"42457e641136fc40f01471221859c45820e64df5","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"12"},{"pid":"0e41af809fb339926aff719ac4da8b0b691e4495","tid":1476062,"uid":276827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"13"}]}